name: Nana Yōkai Collection: Nurikabe
description: Nana Yōkai Collection is a series of illustrations, created with the aim of sharing traditional Japanese mythology. In this series, Nana will be personifying herself as different Yōkai (Japanese spirits). Nurikabe appears mysteriously on roads at night and is usually said to be invisible. Nurikabe materializes and blocks the way.  This yokai extends itself, so there is no way to slip around it.
